        <pre>
        <strong>_@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => Model.Client.Name)_</strong> an applicant for the services of Mental Health and if applicable; <br />
        <strong>_@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => Model.Client.LegalGuardian.Name)_</strong> representative/guardian of the above named applicant:
