    </div>
</div>

<div>
    <div class="form-group col-md-8">
        <pre>
            Hereby acknowledge receipt of <strong>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => Model.Client.Clinic.Name)</strong>  Notice of Privacy 
            Practices. This Notice of Privacy Practices provides detailed information about how 
            <strong>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => Model.Client.Clinic.Name)</strong>  may use and disclose my protected health and confidential 
